OL,6,GThe BBC appears to inadvertently
OL,7,Gadmitted it's throwing millions of
OL,8,Gviewers into a regional news black
OL,9,Ghole, as local news programmes from
OL,10,GCambridge and Oxford air their final
OL,11,Gbulletins this week.
OL,13,FViewers in Bedfordshire and most of
OL,14,FBuckinghamshire, Northamptonshire plus
OL,15,Fthe northern half of Hertfordshire may
OL,16,Ffeel they have been forgotten about,
OL,17,Faccording to what the broadcaster has
OL,18,Fjust told regulator Ofcom.
OL,3,CRegional BBC viewers thrown into a
OL,4,Cblack hole
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G1/11
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
