SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F345A1672362523
OL,6,FWhile Ofcom doesn't have a say on how
OL,7,Fthe BBC regions are structured, it does
OL,8,Fneed to approve changes to BBC quotas
OL,9,Fon regional output in accordance with
OL,10,Fthe BBC Operating Licence. As such, the
OL,11,FBBC has had to tell Ofcom more details
OL,12,Fabout its cuts to regional services.
OL,13,FThis document was published by the
OL,14,Fregulator this week.
OL,16,FIn an explanatory footnote, the BBC
OL,17,Fconfirmed the new single edition Look
OL,18,FEast "will cover Cambridge, Essex,
OL,19,FNorfolk and Suffolk".
OL,3,CRegional BBC viewers thrown into a
OL,4,Cblack hole
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G2/11
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
