OL,6,FAnd South Today will cover "Hampshire,
OL,7,FIsle of Wight, Oxfordshire, West
OL,8,FSussex, much of Dorset and parts of
OL,9,FBerkshire, Surrey and Wiltshire",
OL,10,Fincorporating the area covered by BBC
OL,11,FOxford's TV bulletins.
OL,13,F"Following the changes Look East will
OL,14,Fcover Cambridge, Essex, Norfolk and
OL,15,FSuffolk and South Today will cover
OL,16,FHampshire, Isle of Wight, Oxfordshire,
OL,17,FWest Sussex, much of Dorset and parts
OL,18,Fof Berkshire, Surrey and Wiltshire."
