OL,6,FExplaining the changes further, the BBC
OL,7,Fsaid "news in Cambridgeshire will now
OL,8,Fbe included in Look East (sic)* and
OL,9,Fnews from Oxfordshire in South Today" `
OL,10,Fa statement that completely disregards
OL,11,Fanyone living between Cambridgeshire
OL,12,Fand Oxfordshire, including places such
OL,13,Fas Aylesbury, Bedford, Milton Keynes
OL,14,Fand Northampton.
OL,16,F* News from Cambridgeshire already
OL,17,Fappears on a programme called Look
OL,18,FEast. What the BBC means is the
OL,19,Fremaining Norwich-based edition going
OL,20,Fforward.
OL,3,CRegional BBC viewers thrown into a
OL,4,Cblack hole
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S     G4/11
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
