OL,6,F"While neither the Agreement nor the
OL,7,FOperating Licence specify the number of
OL,8,Fseparate regions, the existing quota is
OL,9,Fbased on the current cumulative level
OL,10,Fof opts."These changes will lead to no
OL,11,Freduction in the volume of news
OL,12,Favailable to viewers at home, who will
OL,13,Finstead receive news from a slightly
OL,14,Fbroader region than previously.
OL,3,CRegional BBC viewers thrown into a
