OL,6,F"That is, news in Cambridgeshire will
OL,7,Fnow be included in Look East and news
OL,8,Ffrom Oxfordshire in South
OL,9,FToday."Collectively, these changes will
OL,10,Freduce the total volume of local news
OL,11,Fbroadcast by the BBC by about 260 hours
OL,12,Fper year (of which about 190 hours in
OL,13,FPeak Viewing Time) but will not impact
OL,14,Fon our audiences' experience of the
OL,15,Fimportant coverage from these areas."
