OL,6,FThe transmitter that carried the
OL,7,FCambridge edition of Look East is Sandy
OL,8,FHeath, firmly in Bedfordshire.
OL,9,FPostcodes in these areas are assigned
OL,10,Fto BBC One East and ITV Anglia on Sky
OL,11,Fand Freesat.
OL,13,FEditorially most areas were covered by
OL,14,FLook East from Cambridge. Places near
OL,15,Fthe Oxfordshire/Buckinghamshire border
OL,16,Fwere covered by BBC Oxford, where
OL,17,Fsignals from the Oxford (Beckley)
OL,18,Ftransmitter penetrates across the
OL,19,FAylesbury area.
