OL,6,FAffected viewers will now see news from
OL,7,Feither Southampton or Norwich.
OL,9,FRealistically, news stories from places
OL,10,Flike Northampton, Milton Keynes,
OL,11,FAylesbury or Bedford will continue to
OL,12,Fbe covered by one of the replacement
OL,13,Fservices, regardless of what the BBC
OL,14,Fhas said and they will probably get
OL,15,Fsome prominence initially in an attempt
OL,16,Fto ease the transition.
