OL,6,FBut ultimately they will compete
OL,7,Fagainst stories from over 100 miles
OL,8,Faway for airtime on programmes that
OL,9,Fthemselves have seen big cuts in
OL,10,Fpresenter and reporter numbers in the
OL,11,Flast two years.
OL,13,FIs the BBC creating its own narrative,
OL,14,Ftrying to minimise the impact to the
OL,15,Fregulator and parliamentarians? To
OL,16,Fframe this as affecting a much smaller
OL,17,Fgeographical area than it actually is?
OL,18,FOr does someone not have a map of the
OL,19,FBBC regions?
