OL,6,FTo put it in perspective, the number of
OL,7,Fpeople in the affected counties is
OL,8,Fgreater than the number of people
OL,9,Fliving in some of the BBC's other
OL,10,Fbroadcast regions.
OL,12,FAs Roger Mosey, former head of BBC News
OL,13,Fput it: "...yes, the BBC needs to save
